## Architecture

- **Framework:** Tauri 2.x (Rust backend + WebView frontend)
- **Frontend:** React 18.3.1 + Vite 5.4.18 + TypeScript 5.7.3 + Tailwind CSS 3.4.22 + shadcn/ui + Zustand 4.5.7
- **Backend:** Rust (alarm engine, audio, notifications, storage)
- **Database:** Single SQLite file (rusqlite 0.32.1 + refinery 0.8.14 migrations, WAL mode)
- **Tables:** Alarms, AlarmGroups, Settings, SnoozeState, AlarmEvents (all PascalCase)
- **Domain enums:** 13 TypeScript + Rust enums (RepeatType, ChallengeType, AlarmEventType, SortField, etc.)
- **Error enums:** AlarmAppError (13 variants) + WebhookError (4 variants) with thiserror 2.0.12
- **State management:** Zustand — useAlarmStore, useOverlayStore, useSettingsStore
- **All dependencies pinned with `=x.y.z`** — see `10-dependency-lock.md`

